{"tid":719366,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【空置稅逼近】元朗村屋劈價近550萬放盤 叫價2,228萬","createTime":"2018-06-27T11:10:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-28T01:34:03.000Z","uid":174649,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"00f42d87ddbcc295a2cd95f47479519635a446ba","tid":719366,"uid":174649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T11:10:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180627/large/1530097261_9cba.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180627%2Flarge%2F1530097261_9cba.jpg&h=d7e221a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n空置稅有機會本周推出，除了大型發展商近期積極推售手上現樓貨尾外，部分私人持有的新界一手村屋亦怕空置稅殺到而劈價放盤。一手住宅銷售網顯示，元朗八鄉元崗251號及252號村屋，今日分別劈價19.8%及15.5%，其中元崗251號實用面積2,029方呎，花園面積1,400方呎，天台面積681方呎，於2015年12月落成，今年3月放盤叫價2,776.8萬元，呎價13,686元，今日減價549萬元至2,228萬元，呎價10,981元，減幅高達19.8%。<br />\n<br />\n另一伙為元崗252號，實用面積2,029方呎，花園面積1,024方呎，天台面積681方呎，於2016年1月落成，原叫價2,518萬元，呎價12,410元，今日減價380萬元至2,128萬元，呎價10,488元。"},{"pid":"d81f45352bfcc2f18534406a5cef79fa067c0532","tid":719366,"uid":171446,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T11:15:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b4dd5b21a05bcbc9afe87da62b6ca56d8e297736","tid":719366,"uid":72173,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T11:46:20.000Z","msg":"如果無得賣/收租<br />\n真係寧願住番市區算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57d52746d781a617eb2d2f5cac1c50d9ea82e425","tid":719366,"uid":40089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T11:59:45.000Z","msg":"大尺數過萬蚊尺<br />\n咁入既位都過萬蚊尺<br />\n<br />\n毒果又想呃人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bcaa37301683c4367c3354d9708935611249961","tid":719366,"uid":109386,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T14:10:18.000Z","msg":"屌你老母，村屋過萬蚊呎，忽撚大左？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"